<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 20:21:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>两名共和党政策制定者表示，美国对华政策必须从管理竞争转向冷战立场</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3258561/us-policy-china-must-pivot-cold-war-stance-managing-competition-two-republican-policymakers-say?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>乔·拜登被指控优先考虑与北京领导人的“短期解冻”，而牺牲了“对其恶意战略的长期胜利”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 17:35:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3258561/us-policy-china-must-pivot-cold-war-stance-managing-competition-two-republican-policymakers-say?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国计划到2027年实现国产飞机发动机和大型商用飞机的大规模设备升级</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3258534/china-eyes-home-grown-aircraft-engine-larger-commercial-planes-big-equipment-upgrades-2027?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着外部压力的加大，北京方面更加重视增强“生产力”，这被认为有助于中国实现航空自给自足。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3258534/china-eyes-home-grown-aircraft-engine-larger-commercial-planes-big-equipment-upgrades-2027?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国将听取美国宇航局科学家和其他研究人员的建议，研究嫦娥五号月球样本</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3258530/china-hear-pitches-nasa-scientist-other-researchers-study-change-5-lunar-samples?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国航天局将于本月晚些时候听取国际建议，借用这些材料进行研究。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3258530/china-hear-pitches-nasa-scientist-other-researchers-study-change-5-lunar-samples?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国科学家称，陨石表明小行星灶神星可能曾经拥有像早期月球一样的岩浆湖</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3258529/meteorite-suggests-asteroid-vesta-may-once-have-had-magma-lake-just-early-moon-say-chinese?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>研究人员发现了第一个证据，表明小行星带第二大天体灶神星的表面曾经被熔岩覆盖。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3258529/meteorite-suggests-asteroid-vesta-may-once-have-had-magma-lake-just-early-moon-say-chinese?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰战争：中国必须超越言辞，成为和平缔造者</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/world-opinion/article/3258470/ukraine-war-china-must-go-beyond-rhetoric-emerge-peacemaker?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国特使李辉表示，北京与俄罗斯和乌克兰的友谊有助于两国​​之间的调解。然而，为了认真对待其缔造和平的雄心，中国应该与美国和其他北约成员国密切合作，并对俄罗斯施加更多压力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/world-opinion/article/3258470/ukraine-war-china-must-go-beyond-rhetoric-emerge-peacemaker?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国取消部分电信服务所有权上限，吸引外资复苏</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3258531/china-scraps-ownership-caps-some-telecoms-services-courting-foreign-capital-resurgence?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国公布了针对某些电信服务的新外资所有权规定，此举旨在为中国努力实现广泛的经济目标创造投资和信心。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3258531/china-scraps-ownership-caps-some-telecoms-services-courting-foreign-capital-resurgence?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国军事研究人员专注于人工智能驱动的海军和太空作战，以“赢得未来战争”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3258503/chinese-military-researchers-zero-ai-driven-navy-space-combat-win-future-wars?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>共产党的一份重要报纸《学习时报》发表了解放军专家关于新兴武器技术以占领战略制高点的系列文章。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 11:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3258503/chinese-military-researchers-zero-ai-driven-navy-space-combat-win-future-wars?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>报告称，尽管全球投资大幅下滑，但中国去年每周仍新增 1 家独角兽公司，部分原因是人工智能热潮</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3258526/china-added-one-unicorn-week-last-year-despite-slumping-global-investments-thanks-partly-ai-frenzy?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在地缘政治紧张局势加剧的情况下，投资中国独角兽企业的前 30 名投资者大多数都位于中国境内。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:30:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3258526/china-added-one-unicorn-week-last-year-despite-slumping-global-investments-thanks-partly-ai-frenzy?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>德国企业调查称中国对外国企业造成“不公平竞争”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3258513/china-creating-unfair-competition-foreign-players-german-firms-say-survey?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在中国经营的德国企业表示，他们面临“不公平竞争”，这使得德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨访华之前两国之间本已紧张的关系变得更加复杂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3258513/china-creating-unfair-competition-foreign-players-german-firms-say-survey?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>在美国和日本密切关注中国之际，拜登与岸田会面将取得“显着”规模的成果：内部人士</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3258464/us-and-japan-keep-eye-china-biden-kishida-meeting-yield-outcomes-remarkable-scale-insiders?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国官员承认，外国对特朗普就任总统后印太战略下的新伙伴关系能否持续感到担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3258464/us-and-japan-keep-eye-china-biden-kishida-meeting-yield-outcomes-remarkable-scale-insiders?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>习近平主席在历史性的北京会谈中告诉台湾马英九，没有解决不了的问题</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258424/president-xi-jinping-meets-taiwans-ma-ying-jeou-historic-first-9-years-after-landmark-singapore?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>习近平表示，“外国干涉”无法阻止“家人团聚”的历史趋势，马英九成为第一位与大陆最高领导人会面的现任或前台湾总统。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258424/president-xi-jinping-meets-taiwans-ma-ying-jeou-historic-first-9-years-after-landmark-singapore?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>惠誉下调信用前景后中国反击，北京称地方债务风险可控</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3258479/china-hits-back-after-fitch-ratings-downgrades-credit-outlook-beijing-says-local-debt-risks-are?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>财政部表示，出于对房地产和公共财政压力的担忧，惠誉评级将中国主权债务前景从稳定调整为负面，令人“遗憾”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 05:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3258479/china-hits-back-after-fitch-ratings-downgrades-credit-outlook-beijing-says-local-debt-risks-are?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>“习惯勒紧裤腰带”：中国地方政府和共产党机构如何拥抱削减成本的文化</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258472/get-used-tighter-belts-how-chinas-local-governments-and-party-bodies-are-embracing-cost-cutting?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>为了展示紧缩政策，围绕政府车辆的使用、资源使用、未经授权的办公室打印和瓶装水的新规则正在出台。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 05:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258472/get-used-tighter-belts-how-chinas-local-governments-and-party-bodies-are-embracing-cost-cutting?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>微软暴雪与网易恢复合作伙伴关系，将《魔兽世界》带回中国玩家的怀抱</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3258471/microsofts-blizzard-resumes-netease-partnership-bringing-world-warcraft-back-chinese-players-after?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>暴雪娱乐在新东家微软的领导下恢复了与网易的合作关系，标志着一年多前曾激烈破裂的一项长期存在的美中视频游戏协议的复兴。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 05:10:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3258471/microsofts-blizza